WEBVTT

01:17:07.541 --> 01:17:11.499
Mary Curie, after the
radiation poisoning, right?

01:17:12.124 --> 01:17:12.874
I'm from the best.

01:17:13.374 --> 01:17:14.291
[LAUGH]

01:17:15.624 --> 01:17:16.499
We made a great kid.

01:17:17.499 --> 01:17:18.916
Yeah, we did.

01:17:25.374 --> 01:17:28.541
I know you can't see me, but
I chicken on you both all the time.

01:17:29.624 --> 01:17:31.999
And I don't want to be the
reason that drove you to a party.

01:17:32.999 --> 01:17:33.749
You need each other.

01:17:34.791 --> 01:17:35.916
You make each other better.

01:17:37.541 --> 01:17:38.249
Always have.

01:17:40.124 --> 01:17:40.624
[NOISE]

01:17:42.374 --> 01:17:43.874
We got to get back to Winter River.

01:17:44.624 --> 01:17:46.374
You can't leave them
till Esther gets your life back.

01:17:47.124 --> 01:17:47.624
Let's go.

01:17:50.749 --> 01:17:53.249
The gold patrol
found the bridge and sealed it.

01:17:53.791 --> 01:17:56.749
Any sign of Mr.
Beetlejuice or the flesh bag?

01:17:56.999 --> 01:17:59.874
Still looking, but we did
find something that might help.
